'''Dokma''' were small, timid [[gastropod]]s<ref name="CargoBay">[[Star Wars: Cargo Bay|''Star Wars'': Cargo Bay]]</ref> native to [[Atollon]]. Often preyed upon by the [[spider]]-like [[krykna]], they had protective shells and two [[eye]]stalks. [[Garazeb Orrelios]] nicknamed them "[[Lasat (language)|'''bogans''']]."<ref name="The Mystery of Chopper Base" /> According to [[Volt Vescuso]], the amount of [[milk]] a dokma drank was not to be underestimated.<ref name="A Crash of Fate">''[[A Crash of Fate]]''</ref>

